out to things like Substack, to newsletters,

00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:46.500
Patreon, PayWorld Gardens.

00:01:46.550 --> 00:01:49.110
But AppProtocol is a way for them to native

00:01:49.110 --> 00:01:53.000
ly own that audience where they actually get discovered.

