Actually, this is...

00:22:37.050 --> 00:22:39.160
I'm glad you're asking a question because I was about

00:22:39.160 --> 00:22:43.900
to reference your most recent post and proposal about more artist-

00:22:43.900 --> 00:22:46.270
specific metadata on AppRoto.

00:22:46.310 --> 00:22:48.040
So, yeah, we'd love to hear it.

00:22:48.070 --> 00:22:50.800
Thank you that you're introduced because...

00:22:50.830 --> 00:22:52.580
And if you want to talk about what you...

00:22:52.610 --> 00:22:52.760
Yeah.

00:22:52.790 --> 00:22:53.900
Talk about that, please.

