00:28:02.710 --> 00:28:05.810
And as a result, a lot more valuable to the AI

00:28:05.810 --> 00:28:06.880
model providers.

00:28:06.910 --> 00:28:09.380
And so, you know, while we haven't, you

00:28:09.380 --> 00:28:12.940
know, figured out an AI interface for social yet, I

00:28:12.970 --> 00:28:16.200
think we still, you know, swipe through the short form

00:28:16.200 --> 00:28:16.910
video reels.

00:28:17.290 --> 00:28:20.050
And, you know, we haven't really, AI hasn

00:28:20.060 --> 00:28:24.550
't really solved the interface for social in an AI native way

00:28:24.550 --> 00:28:24.770
.

00:28:24.810 --> 00:28:27.600
Like Sora just died last week, right?

00:28:27.630 --> 00:28:33.510
It will be interesting to see how this business model evolves for

00:28:33.520 --> 00:28:34.460
publishers.

00:28:34.490 --> 00:28:38.620
And I think micropayments will be a really big

00:28:38.630 --> 00:28:39.240
piece of it.

00:28:39.250 --> 00:28:41.920
Anything to add there?

