I think, yeah, we're all excited for that kind

00:28:54.900 --> 00:28:57.580
of, there's a big kind of sea change coming for

00:28:57.730 --> 00:29:00.990
creators in terms of how much power and the power dynamics there

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:01.740
with creators.

